    public class Divider
extends ListItem
    Horizontal divider for navigation menus.

    UiBinder Usage:

     <b:NavList>
     <b:NavLink>Link before divider</b:NavLink>
     <b:Divider />
     <b:NavLink>Link after divider</b:NavLink>
 </b:NavList>

    Since:
    2.0.4.0
    Author:
    Dominik Mayer
    See Also:
    Bootstrap documentation, NavList, WellNavList, Dropdown, VerticalDivider
